 <s1 title="Mailing List Archives">
  <p>
   There are a number of mailing list archives available. Email 
   <link href="mailto:cocoon-users@xml.apache.org">cocoon-users@xml.apache.org</link> if you
   know of more.
  </p>

  <table>
   <tr>
    <th>Address</th>
